"Zone drafting" isnt to make things more competitive, its to keep things organized so there are less problems all around.

Its a good habit to pick up.

There may not be more than one pack between players.

if a pack builds up then "tap" the pile

don't make a train of piles


**** Draft basics ****
Drafting is idea for 8 players but isnt strick to it it just allows for elimiation when doing the typcial 3 rounds

3 packs
starting with left pick 2 cards (or 1)

